      <title>由于美国降息可能推迟，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管乐观的中国贸易数据预示着全球最大石油进口国的需求良好，但由于对美国降息可能推迟的预期限制了油价周四下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</guid>
